---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About ByteLite LLC - Building HeartStrings, ByteLite, and Deep Kore"
  description="ByteLite LLC builds products people actually want. HeartStrings Play is the first public launch product. HeartStrings sparked ByteLite. ByteLite powers the app. Deep Kore drives future intelligence. Founder: Tash Broadwater, Helena MT."
  keywords={["ByteLite LLC", "HeartStrings Play", "HeartStrings App", "ByteLite", "Deep Kore", "Tash Broadwater", "Helena MT", "compression technology"]}
  schemaType="Organization"
>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Company Story -->
      <div class="story-section">
        <h2>ByteLite LLC</h2>
        <div class="story-content">
          <p class="lead">
            ByteLite LLC is a product company built in Helena, MT by founder Tash Broadwater.
            We build products people actually want, backed by infrastructure we built ourselves.
          </p>

          <blockquote>
            "HeartStrings was the original idea. ByteLite is what we built to make it possible."
          </blockquote>

          <p>
            In 2024, while developing HeartStrings -- a relationship intelligence platform -- founder Tash Broadwater
            hit a fundamental constraint: AI models demanded storage and compute that put the product out of reach for
            an independent team. The question that followed became ByteLite.
          </p>

          <p>
            HeartStrings Play is the first public launch product. A premium social board game that does not require
            any backend infrastructure to deliver a real experience right now. The HeartStrings App follows -- powered
            by ByteLite compression and Deep Kore intelligence. The ecosystem is designed from the outside in:
            consumer product first, infrastructure supporting it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ecosystem Overview -->
      <div class="ecosystem-section">
        <h2>The Ecosystem</h2>
        <div class="ecosystem-grid">

          <div class="eco-card play">
            <div class="eco-header">
              <h3>HeartStrings Play</h3>
              <span class="badge launch">Launch Product</span>
            </div>
            <p>A premium social board game for couples, dates, and intimate gatherings. Six escalating card tiers. AIya and AIon as guides. The first public-facing product from ByteLite LLC.</p>
            <a href="/heartstrings" class="eco-link play">See HeartStrings Play</a>
          </div>

          <div class="eco-card app">
            <div class="eco-header">
              <h3>HeartStrings App</h3>
              <span class="badge indev">In Development</span>
            </div>
            <p>The digital companion. Profiles, match rationale, and guided interaction powered by AIya and AIon. Connects game sessions to digital continuity. Built on ByteLite infrastructure.</p>
            <a href="/heartstrings-app" class="eco-link app">See the App</a>
          </div>

          <div class="eco-card bytelite">
            <div class="eco-header">
              <h3>ByteLite</h3>
              <span class="badge active">Active Engineering</span>
            </div>
            <p>The infrastructure layer. Structural compression using dictionary-cascade architecture. Patent US 63/807,027. Born from the storage problem HeartStrings surfaced in 2024.</p>
            <a href="/technology" class="eco-link bytelite">See ByteLite</a>
          </div>

          <div class="eco-card deepkore">
            <div class="eco-header">
              <h3>Deep Kore / AIya</h3>
              <span class="badge research">Research</span>
            </div>
            <p>The intelligence and governance layer. AIya and AIon are its first public face. Genesis Goal Keeper safety framework governs all research. Blueprint-stage architecture building carefully.</p>
            <a href="/deepkore" class="eco-link deepkore">See Deep Kore</a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission -->
      <div class="mission-section">
        <div class="mission-card">
          <h3>What We Are Building</h3>
          <p>
            We are building a consumer product ecosystem where every layer is owned by the team.
            HeartStrings Play is the front door. The app is the expansion. ByteLite is the engine underneath.
            Deep Kore is the long bet on what intelligent infrastructure can become.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-card">
          <h3>Why This Approach</h3>
          <p>
            The launch product -- HeartStrings Play -- requires no backend. It works now. It generates interest.
            It creates the context the app and the ecosystem need to matter to real people.
            Infrastructure without a product is just research. We built both.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Project Status -->
      <div class="status-section">
        <h2>Project Status</h2>
        <div class="status-grid">

          <div class="status-card heartstrings-play">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>HeartStrings Play</h3>
              <span class="status-badge launch">Launch Product</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              Game design is complete. Board, card tiers, and character design are finalized.
              Physical prototype production is in progress. Manufacturing and retail launch planned
              once prototype is validated.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill heartstrings-play" style="width: 70%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="status-card heartstrings-app">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>HeartStrings App</h3>
              <span class="status-badge indev">In Development</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              UI design system and login screens are designed. Profile and match engine
              under active development. AIya and AIon integration in progress.
              First access will be for HeartStrings Play purchasers.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill heartstrings-app" style="width: 35%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="status-card bytelite">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>ByteLite Compression</h3>
              <span class="status-badge active">Active Development</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              Dictionary-cascade compression in advanced development. Patent US 63/807,027 filed.
              Browser demo live at /demo. Broader verification application in development.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill bytelite" style="width: 80%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="status-card deepkore">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>Deep Kore / AIya</h3>
              <span class="status-badge research">Research Phase</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              Blueprint-stage architecture research. Genesis Goal Keeper safety framework operational.
              AIya and AIon character layer active. Research is intentionally careful and governed.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill deepkore" style="width: 35%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder -->
      <div class="founder-section">
        <h2>Founder</h2>
        <div class="founder-card">
          <h3>Tash Broadwater, Founder and CEO</h3>
          <p>
            Software engineer and compression researcher based in Helena, MT. 15+ years optimizing data systems.
            Specializes in algorithmic design and edge AI systems. Built ByteLite to solve the storage problem
            that HeartStrings surfaced. Building the ecosystem from the consumer product layer down.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h3>Get Involved</h3>
        <p>Follow HeartStrings Play development. Express interest in the app. Discuss ByteLite enterprise integration.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/heartstrings" class="btn btn-pink">HeartStrings Play</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get In Touch</a>
          <a href="/status" class="btn btn-secondary">View Status</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-darker);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Story Section */
  .story-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .story-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #EC4899;
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #EC4899;
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.05);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  /* Ecosystem Section */
  .ecosystem-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .ecosystem-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .ecosystem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .eco-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .eco-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }

  .eco-card.play    { border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.3); }
  .eco-card.app     { border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.25); }
  .eco-card.bytelite { border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); }
  .eco-card.deepkore { border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2); }

  .eco-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .eco-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .eco-card.play h3    { color: #EC4899; }
  .eco-card.app h3     { color: #FB7185; }
  .eco-card.bytelite h3 { color: #00D4FF; }
  .eco-card.deepkore h3 { color: #A855F7; }

  .badge {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .badge.launch  { background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15); color: #EC4899; border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4); }
  .badge.indev   { background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1); color: #A855F7; border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3); }
  .badge.active  { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1); color: #22C55E; border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3); }
  .badge.research { background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1); color: #A855F7; border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3); }

  .eco-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .eco-link {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .eco-link.play    { color: #EC4899; }
  .eco-link.app     { color: #FB7185; }
  .eco-link.bytelite { color: #00D4FF; }
  .eco-link.deepkore { color: #A855F7; }
  .eco-link:hover { opacity: 0.75; }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .mission-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .mission-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .mission-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .mission-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  /* Status Section */
  .status-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .status-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .status-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .status-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .status-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .status-card.heartstrings-play { border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.25); }
  .status-card.heartstrings-app  { border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.2); }
  .status-card.bytelite          { border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); }
  .status-card.deepkore          { border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2); }

  .status-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .status-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .status-card.heartstrings-play .status-header h3 { color: #EC4899; }
  .status-card.heartstrings-app .status-header h3  { color: #FB7185; }
  .status-card.bytelite .status-header h3          { color: #00D4FF; }
  .status-card.deepkore .status-header h3          { color: #A855F7; }

  .status-badge {
    padding: 0.2rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .status-badge.launch  { background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15); color: #EC4899; border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4); }
  .status-badge.indev   { background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1); color: #A855F7; border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3); }
  .status-badge.active  { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.12); color: #00D4FF; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4); }
  .status-badge.research { background: rgba(255, 171, 0, 0.12); color: #FFAB00; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 171, 0, 0.3); }

  .status-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    height: 6px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .progress-fill.heartstrings-play { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #EC4899, #FB7185); }
  .progress-fill.heartstrings-app  { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FB7185, #A855F7); }
  .progress-fill.bytelite          { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00D4FF, #0099CC); }
  .progress-fill.deepkore          { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #A855F7, #FF006E); }

  /* Founder */
  .founder-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .founder-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .founder-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .founder-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .founder-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .btn-pink {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EC4899 0%, #BE185D 100%);
    color: white;
  }
  .btn-pink:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4); }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #00B8E6; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.25);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.5); color: #E0E0E0; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ecosystem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .mission-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .status-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

    .status-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
